            <h2>What is Answer Engine Optimisation?</h2>
            <p>Answer Engine Optimisation focuses on structuring content to appear in direct answer formats in search results. This includes featured snippets, knowledge panels and AI-generated answer boxes.</p>
            <p>Search engines increasingly provide direct answers to queries rather than simply listing links. AEO adapts your content to be selected for these positions.</p>
            <p>The practical outcome is that your content becomes the source that search engines extract and display when users ask questions related to your expertise or services.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- How AEO Works Section -->
